-go-back-to-school\/?utm_content=hm-back-to-school\">&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"donate-card animate-card\"><img class=\"donate-card-img\" src=\"\/wp-content\/themes\/cry\/images\/help-stop-child-labour.jpg\" alt=\"CRY donate image\"\/><div class=\"donate-card-info\"><span class=\"donate-card-subtitle\">Stop Child Labour<\/span><h3 class=\"donate-card-title\">Help children go to school instead<\/h3>\n<p><a class=\"btn donate-btn\" href=\"\/help-children-learn-not-earn\/?utm_content=hm-acld\">&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"donate-card animate-card\"><img class=\"donate-card-img\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/help-expecting-mothers-and-their-babies-survive.jpg\" alt=\"CRY donate image\"\/>\n\n<div class=\"donate-card-info\"><span class=\"donate-card-subtitle\">Help Expecting Mothers<\/span>\n\n<h3 class=\"donate-card-title\">Provide nutritional care for pregnant mothers<\/h3>\n<p><a class=\"btn donate-btn\" href=\"\/help-expecting-mothers-and-their-babies-survive\/?utm_content=hm\">&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"donate-card animate-card\"><img class=\"donate-card-img\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/bridge-the-education-gap.jpg\" alt=\"CRY donate image\"\/>\n\n<div class=\"donate-card-info\"><span class=\"donate-card-subtitle\">Bridge The Education Gap<\/span>\n\n<h3 class=\"donate-card-title\">Help children continue their education<\/h3>\n<p><a class=\"btn donate-btn\" href=\"\/help-bridge-the-education-gap\">&nbsp;<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"donate-card animate-card\"><img class=\"donate-card-img\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/help-underweight-babies-survive-sm.jpg\" alt=\"CRY donate image\"\/>\n\n<div class=\"donate-card-info\"><span class=\"donate-card-subtitle\">Help Underweight Babies Survive<\/span>\n\n<h3 class=\"donate-card-title\">Ensure proper nutrition for underweight babies<\/h3>\n<p><a class=\"btn donate-btn\" href=\"\/help-underweight-babies-survive\/?utm_conte